://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2Fdonation&d=q18Y%2F9yBacX5GGPSgvrSC%2BSCO5RJLUOM1IbOSdmZk8c%3D&h=117b8f4e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk/donation</a><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vBAj6Qv.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvBAj6Qv.gif&h=8056e3fd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GFOJO3Q.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGFOJO3Q.gif&h=92e11c5f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NOtUVJR.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNOtUVJR.gif&h=eaa393bf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CLA4yvw.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCLA4yvw.gif&h=3a86806f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qFOqhXb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqFOqhXb.gif&h=b24b8c4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f98a5919b6c180561ed6243c2ea6742c7bc69b1","tid":1303682,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T11:50:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c67467045b3c78e7b299873cd68b772daf1bc3c","tid":1303682,"uid":160605,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T11:52:35.000Z","msg":"講撚左唔好提獨，原本提一國兩制都冇乜野。一提獨就變晒膠"},{"pid":"8b9853814795a7dca9a1e9fbd8c6f825a8a9adc0","tid":1303682,"uid":133680,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"6c67467045b3c78e7b299873cd68b772daf1bc3c","tid":1303682,"uid":160605,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T11:52:35.000Z","msg":"講撚左唔好提獨，原本提一國兩制都冇乜野。一提獨就變晒膠"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T11:53:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bD6SOss.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbD6SOss.jpg&h=db31